vote.title: A resolution authorizing (1) an increase in the joint election agreement and election services contract between the City of Dallas and Collin County for the November 8, 2022 special election in an amount not to exceed $5,047.47, from $50,246.94 to $55,294.41; and (2) a reimbursement of funding in an amount not to exceed $5,047.47 from the Convention center Capital Construction Fund to the General Fund - Not to exceed $5,047.47, from $50,246.94 to $55,294.41 - Financing:  Convention Center Capital Construction Fund (see Fiscal Information)
